FBIS3-52174 "drnes001_l_94016" FBIS-NES-94-001 Document Type:Daily Report 3 Jan 1994 ISRAEL Vatican Representative Signs Recognition Accord LD3012145693 Rome RAI Televideo Teletext in Italian 1421 GMT 30 Dec 93 LD3012145693 Rome RAI Televideo Teletext Language: Italian Article Type:BFN [Text] The accord on mutual recognition between the Vatican and Israel was signed at 1500, in the Foreign Ministry in Jerusalem. Monsignor Claudio Celli, the Vatican foreign affairs under-secretary, signed the agreement behalf of the Holy See, as did Deputy Foreign Minister Beilin for the State of Israel.
